author: John S
title: John S
text: The only vendor found that had exactly what I wanted for my framing project. I have used Nielsen frames before, however the miter cuts on my frame were superior to any other I have received from any previous supplier. The packaging was superior also, insuring my frame and acrylic arrived in perfect condition. Thank you. I will definitely be a return customer.
